# 📊 Resilience Patterns Comparison

| Pattern         | Purpose                           | Best For                         | Handles                  | Key Benefit                 |
| --------------- | --------------------------------- | -------------------------------- | ------------------------ | --------------------------- |
| Retry           | Reattempt failed operations       | Temporary failures               | Timeouts, network issues | Automatic recovery          |
| DLQ             | Store permanently failed messages | Message processing               | Invalid messages         | Prevents queue blockage     |
| Circuit Breaker | Stop calls to failing services    | Service-to-service communication | Service outages          | Prevents cascading failures |

